{"tid":1162198,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【47秒K.O.】格鬥狂人出招 打斷詠春點穴大師鼻樑","createTime":"2019-05-19T16:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T01:49:15.000Z","uid":103156,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a3a8c3bfeab4e15ace62b826b788c555ab331f47","tid":1162198,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:58:43.000Z","msg":"【47秒K.O.】格鬥狂人出招 打斷詠春點穴大師鼻樑<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190519&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59618990\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190519%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59618990&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ19ekL701Gi2Y7kfdl15EDb4%3D&h=1d4f1f6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190519%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59618990&h=f84ffc30\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190519&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59618990</a><br />\n<br />\n內地「格鬥狂人」<span style=\"color: red;\">徐曉冬近日對決詠春點穴大師呂剛，僅用了47秒，徐曉冬就打斷呂剛鼻樑獲勝。</span><br />\n<br />\n據《搏擊江湖》指出，今日凌晨，在新疆舉辦的「絲路英雄&amp;終極勇士　世界格鬥精英賽」賽事中，上演了徐曉冬出戰詠春大師呂剛的比賽，開賽沒多久徐曉冬一頓組合拳，僅花了47秒，就將呂剛擯出局，而且打斷了對手的鼻樑，呂剛不得入院治療。<br />\n<br />\n這場比賽源於一次網絡約戰，<span style=\"color: red;\">號稱是葉問徒孫，練過兩儀拳和詠春拳，並且會點穴神功的呂剛</span>，一直在網上向徐曉冬叫陣，徐曉冬表示他聯絡過香港詠春總部，對方表示沒有呂剛這號人物，因此這次屬於「打騙子」。<br />\n<br />\nYou tube 有片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7R5VHb79pks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7R5VHb79pks&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ19ekL701Gi2Y7kfdl15EDb4%3D&h=0608ad0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7R5VHb79pks</a>"},{"pid":"463d703820bbae98b56ea84191ac051ba1694ed0","tid":1162198,"uid":103156,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpkkH3r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpkkH3r.png&h=f41e5d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DZ3yiBF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDZ3yiBF.png&h=975fd2a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ea98e37fd3abd78100ec82bf5b8aa591ba99363","tid":1162198,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da39e21a47a88339d2d683cfbbb9ff7824ac382","tid":1162198,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:06:32.000Z","msg":"戇鳩"},{"pid":"69c79837cdaa9df0d5c09d3dd44efa1f73332614","tid":1162198,"uid":68821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c3c289b82032972eae3bc0aaecbb8ada07f1e3","tid":1162198,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:10:03.000Z","msg":"接到香港連勝之子三拳再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb6a7577024ec47c98dc72eb8f6b7a5edbec3e7","tid":1162198,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26c3c289b82032972eae3bc0aaecbb8ada07f1e3","tid":1162198,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:10:03.000Z","msg":"接到香港連勝之子三拳再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ce75f2b61a9758cbef896376ec52a46b78f9ee","tid":1162198,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:18:55.000Z","msg":"李嘉幾時同佢打"},{"pid":"b8e16986e66bd9ecb1e631dbac872dcad47f6af9","tid":1162198,"uid":67208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:22:18.000Z","msg":"磅數都唔啱"},{"pid":"551fc02ede4f2daa48a75a5f7db214eb8ec0f5ff","tid":1162198,"uid":103156,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:24:24.000Z","msg":"賽前報道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">詠春點穴大師呂剛手段多樣還會暗器，用一張撲克就能幹掉徐曉冬？</span><br />\n (2019-03-11 由 楊華評論 發表于運動)<br />\n<br />\n呂剛大師英姿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQtyiEK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQtyiEK.jpg&h=fc2cc36b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nCV49Mq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnCV49Mq.jpg&h=828b88ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kO8iuMr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkO8iuMr.jpg&h=e4d290a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詠春大師呂剛和格鬥狂人徐曉冬簽訂了比賽合同，著名拳評家李田友認為，與太極雷雷、詠春丁浩、里合腿田野不同，<span style=\"color: red;\">呂剛有系統的傳統武術學習經歷，並且是葉問宗師的正牌徒孫，實力遠遠超乎大家的想像，甚至有可能爆冷KO徐曉冬。</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n據報道，呂剛出生於湖北，自幼酷愛武術，2007年到北京拜一代宗師葉問長子葉准大陸弟子王德生師父練習詠春拳，呂剛2010年創辦溫州詠春國術館，隨後拜世界著名武術家、國際詠春總會會長、葉問宗師關門弟子，詠春王武術界的成吉思汗梁挺宗師進修深造詠春技法。<br />\n<br />\n呂剛說他不僅僅<span style=\"color: red;\">擅長詠春，同時擁有兩儀拳點穴絕技，並且學過少林、武當功夫</span>。他介紹說：「我14歲在河北滄州學武，21歲畢業於河北武術學院，1999年奪得雙截棍實戰對打冠軍。2000年奪得河北首武術散打比賽冠軍，2002-2004年在校任教、主教散打、軍警格鬥截拳道、雙截棍。2005年到<span style=\"color: red;\">河南少林寺學，主修、長拳、洪拳、陽光拳、觀音掌、二指禪、氣功、少林棍、劍、九節鞭</span>。隨後北上河南安徽拜兩儀拳研究會會長，兩儀拳正宗傑出傳人高金星宗師，成為高宗師入室弟子，<span style=\"color: red;\">系統研習人體經絡學，點穴，解穴</span>，之後南下湖北武當和武當正宗傳人武當轎子，世界劍術冠軍，陳師行道長<span style=\"color: red;\">學習武當三豐太極，武當太極劍</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n據說丁浩的詠春拳是看電視教學片學的，沒有什麼名師指點，呂剛則不同，作為<span style=\"color: red;\">葉問正牌徒孫</span>，他的技術相當嫻熟。呂剛之前還曾公開挑戰泰拳王播求，希望證明中國功夫的實戰性和殺傷力，但他在網絡直播平台的叫囂，並沒有傳到播求的耳朵里。不過呂剛如果真能KO徐曉冬，那麼勢必會名氣大增，到那時再叫板播求，相信會得到泰拳皇帝的答覆。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，<span style=\"color: red;\">呂剛還掌握了「彈指神功」，就像撲克牌、名片之類的硬紙片，他隨手一扔，就能達到飛刀的效果</span>。在一次直播里，他在四五米開外，用一張撲克割破了啤酒易拉罐，令人非常震驚，他還叫囂<span style=\"color: purple;\">一張撲克就能幹掉徐曉冬</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/sports/ag2ba3j.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fsports%2Fag2ba3j.html&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ19ekL701Gi2Y7kfdl15EDb4%3D&h=73a9b7a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/sports/ag2ba3j.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c7dda51743b484f8ee98c0a6b4129c1137d426","tid":1162198,"uid":145769,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:30:27.000Z","msg":"遠距離點你地笑穴"},{"pid":"529d0725159e3c4b0a3a1e20121fbd519963791f","tid":1162198,"uid":52459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:33:22.000Z","msg":"睇片詠春條友一開始完全無想出拳攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a4007e1d7927bdbbd9349ae36a8934b7da9511","tid":1162198,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"睇得太多葉問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1920a113dc9e92120cf13b227c8ba6011e4f5f59","tid":1162198,"uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呂大師自小習武，練習詠春拳、兩儀拳和彈指神功已有30年之久，最拿手的絕技就是點穴技法，據說<span style=\"color: red;\">只要一擊，就能將年輕力壯的小伙子點倒，瞬間失去運動能力。而與其交過手的人表示，如果被呂剛打中穴位，馬上就會感覺胸口憋悶，就像肺部要爆炸一樣，非常厲害。</span><br />\n<br />\n(原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/news/nga28l8.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fnews%2Fnga28l8.html&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ19ekL701Gi2Y7kfdl15EDb4%3D&h=a7938515\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/news/nga28l8.html</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ebTqUoV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FebTqUoV.jpg&h=7c102ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ysLg03W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FysLg03W.jpg&h=7a9315ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22ec2c2fb6d85a4cf9dd2aea04debeb159f9bfe8","tid":1162198,"uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:50:46.000Z","msg":"據了解，呂剛現在身兼5大神秘武功，分別是<span style=\"color: red;\">點穴拳、詠春拳、彈指神功、金鐘罩和鐵布衫、隔空擊物</span>。我們可以簡單說明一下這5大神秘的武功。點穴拳，大家知道，詠春呂剛已經展示過點穴的威力，只要對準穴位，他輕鬆一拳就可以擊倒對手，甚至對手喪失知覺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />越吹越大，結果 pk.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52c6a732e911fb420e990fbc7e90b87880b6761","tid":1162198,"uid":141681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:55:47.000Z","msg":"挑戰播求 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026299d9a224dca1ce5b865b3848916b3bef2a